      <title>英国机场因液体物品规则改变而陷入混乱并产生额外费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/uk-airport-endures-chaos-and-extra-cost-after-liquid-rule-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯明翰机场斥资 6000 万英镑（7610 万美元）安装最先进的行李扫描仪，旨在通过取消严格的液体限制来加快安检速度。现在，政府的意外限制以及尚未完成的建设工作造成了新设备本应克服的瓶颈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/uk-airport-endures-chaos-and-extra-cost-after-liquid-rule-change</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺和诺德因心脏病药物失败而损失 8.2 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/novo-nordisk-takes-820-million-charge-on-failed-heart-drug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[诺和诺德公司表示，由于停止了去年收购的一种实验性心脏药物的后期研究，该公司将损失约 57 亿丹麦克朗（8.2 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/novo-nordisk-takes-820-million-charge-on-failed-heart-drug</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:14:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国医院数据被盗 暗示黑客攻击比披露的更为严重</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/stolen-data-across-uk-signals-hospital-hack-worse-than-disclosed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦医院攻击事件背后的黑客最近公布了包括英国和爱尔兰孕妇、癌症患者和数千名其他人的个人信息的记录，这表明此次攻击的规模远比当局此前指出的要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/stolen-data-across-uk-signals-hospital-hack-worse-than-disclosed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院支持白宫删除社交媒体帖子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/supreme-court-backs-white-house-on-social-media-post-removal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院在选举年的一项裁决中批准拜登政府与社交媒体公司自由沟通，这增强了政府寻求消除官员认为的错误信息的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/supreme-court-backs-white-house-on-social-media-post-removal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>网络犯罪手段和要求越来越激进</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-26/cybercrime-tactics-and-demands-are-getting-more-aggressive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在勒索手段愈发激进的时代，黑客组织索要巨额报酬并骚扰研究人员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-26/cybercrime-tactics-and-demands-are-getting-more-aggressive</guid>
