    <item>
      <title>Atos 最大投资者放弃救助计划，留下的选择不多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/atos-says-onepoint-has-ended-talks-epei-offers-to-step-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[其最大股东放弃了拯救陷入困境的法国 IT 公司的计划，导致 Atos SE 的救助谈判再次遭受打击，导致该公司的选择越来越少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/atos-says-onepoint-has-ended-talks-epei-offers-to-step-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 06:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度调查发现 Byju’s 未犯欺诈行为，但存在合规漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/probe-finds-byju-s-failed-investors-but-didn-t-commit-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度公司事务部否认 Byju’s 已洗清财务欺诈罪，并称媒体有关相反的报道在事实上“不正确且具有误导性”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/probe-finds-byju-s-failed-investors-but-didn-t-commit-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:54:31 GMT</pubDate>
